						<a class="title" href="javascript:;" onclick="togglePostFold(event,2782686)"></a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/aceofmoxes" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2943332); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2943332&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610227276" alt="Aceofmoxes" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2943332)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/aceofmoxes" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2943332); return false;" >Aceofmoxes</a></span>, <span class="odate time_1491230170 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">03 Apr 2017 14:36</span>
